data.description: Nestled within the townhome community of Holcombs Crossing, in the heart of Roswell, you'll find for this meticulously maintained & updated end unit townhouse! Prepare to be amazed by the wonderful features and amenities this fully updated home has to offer. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the bright and airy atmosphere, thanks to the abundance of natural light that fills every corner of the house. The open concept living area provides the perfect space for entertaining or simply relaxing with your loved ones. The main level offers cozy den, breakfast area, upgraded kitchen, half bath and laundry space. The kitchen has been renovated and boasts modern appliances, quartz countertops and ample storage space in the new cabinetry. Whether you're a seasoned chef or just enjoy cooking occasional meals, this kitchen will surely impress you. The townhome has new engineered flooring on both levels, new light & fans, freshly painted, newer windows and roof and updated bathrooms. The upper level has 2 spacious bedrooms. Each with private en-suites and walk-in closets. The attached 2 car carport provides convenience and additional storage space. But it doesn't end there! This townhouse community also offers amenities. Imagine spending sunny afternoons lounging by the community pool. The community is just minutes away from local shops, restaurants, and parks. Commuting is a breeze, with convenient access to major highways and public transportation. Don't miss the opportunity to make this fully updated end unit townhouse your new home.
